Bobby Barber https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bobby_Barber 0 Bobby Barber (December 18, 1894 – May 24, 1976) was an American actor who appeared in over 100 films. Barber is notable for his work as a foil for Abbott and Costello on and off screen. Bobby_Barber ( December_18_,_1894 – May_24_,_1976 ) was an_American_actor who appeared in over_100_films .
